<T>__{cut to:}
<L>__{interior bulldog gym day}
<A>__{boxers at the bags, a jumping rope, etc... jake and lily stand in front of the king pin, who's dressed in shorts and a t shirt. he wears boxing gloves and headgear. lupus and harlin stand vigil by the sparring ring.}
