<D>__{nothing ventured, nothing gained.}
<C>__{king pin}
<D>__{hey skippy? do i have the word "chump" tattooed on my forehead?}
<C>__{lily}
<D>__{mr . king, i think }
<C>__{jake}
<P>__{(w a look)}
<D>__{hey, i got it! take some mental notes. you just might learn something here.}
