<D>__{come here. feel this.}
<C>__{jake}
<D>__{no thanks. i'm good.}
<C>__{king pin}
<D>__{come here!}
<A>__{the king grabs jake's hand and puts it on his stomach. it just got weirder. now the whole gym has stopped, everyone focused on jake and the king pin.}
